## 🔧 Troubleshooting Quality Checks

### Lint Errors

**Common issues:**
```bash
# Unused imports
→ Remove unused imports from files

# Unused variables  
→ Remove or use variables, or prefix with _ if intentional

# Missing dependencies
→ Add to package.json dependencies array

# ESLint rule violations
→ Fix code to comply with rules
→ OR document why rule should be disabled (rare)
```

### Type Check Errors

**Common issues:**
```bash
# Type mismatches
→ Fix types to match expected interfaces

# Missing type definitions
→ Add proper TypeScript types/interfaces

# Any types used
→ Replace 'any' with proper types

# Import errors
→ Ensure imports have correct types
→ Check convex/_generated/api types
```

### Build Errors

**Common issues:**
```bash
# Next.js compilation errors
→ Fix React component syntax
→ Ensure proper imports

# Module not found
→ Install missing dependencies
→ Fix import paths

# CSS compilation errors
→ Fix CSS syntax
→ Check Tailwind class names

# Environment variables
→ Check .env.local configuration
```

