## 🚀 Automation Integration

### Pre-commit Hook (Future)
```bash
# Automatically run checks before commit
pnpm lint && pnpm type-check && pnpm build || exit 1
```

### CI/CD Pipeline
All these checks run in GitHub Actions:
- Lint failures → Block merge
- Type check failures → Block merge
- Build failures → Block merge

**Local checks catch issues before CI** - saving time and preventing failed builds.

