## 📝 Remember

> **Quality checks are not optional - they are MANDATORY requirements for all code changes.**

> **The 2 minutes spent running checks saves 20+ minutes debugging production issues.**

> **Green checks = Safe to ship. Red checks = Do not commit.**

---

**ENFORCEMENT**: If quality checks are skipped, CI will fail and changes will be rejected. Always run lint, type-check, and build before committing.
